'''Af Sawaaxili''',  loogu dhawaaqo '''{{lang|sw|Kiswahili}}''', waa [[Luqad Bantu|Luqad Bantu]] ah, waxayna luqada koowaad u tahay [[Dadka sawaaxiliga]]. Waa [[lingua franka|lingua frankiga]] [[Bariga Afrika]] iyo  [[Koonfurta hoose ee Afrika]], oo ay ka midtahay [[Kenya]], [[Tanzania]], [[Uganda]], [[Rwanda]], [[Burundi]], meelo ka mid ah [[Malawi]], [[Soomaaliya]], [[Zambia]], [[Mozambique]] iyo [[Jamhuuriyada Dimuqaraadiga Kongo]] (DRC).<ref>{{Cite book|last=Mazrui, Ali Al'Amin.|url=http://worldcat.org/oclc/441402890|title=Swahili state and society : the political economy of an African language|date=1995|publisher=East African Educational Publishers|isbn=0-85255-729-9|oclc=441402890}}</ref><ref>Prins 1961</ref>

Tirada saxda ah ee kuwa ku hadla Sawaaxiliga lama yaqaan. Qiyaaso kaladuwan ayaa horey loosoo bandhigay oo udhaxaysa 100 milyan ilaa 150 milyan oo qof.<ref name=standford>{{cite web | url=http://swahililanguage.stanford.edu | title=HOME – Home | publisher=Swahililanguage.stanford.edu | accessdate=19 July 2016 | quote=After Arabic, Sawaaxiliga waa luqad afrikaan tan ugu wayn laakiin tirada dadka ku hadla ayaa ah aag kale oo ay ka jirto heshiis yar.. Lambarada ugu badan ee lasheegay ayaa ah 50, 80, iyo 100 miliyan oo qof. [...] Tirada dadka u dhashay luqada ayaa ah wax ka yar 20 million.}}</ref>

Af sawaaxiliga waxay luqad qaran u tahay DRC, Kenya, Tanzania, iyo Uganda,  sidoo kale waa mid ka mid ah luqadaha ka shaqeeya [[Ururka Midowga Afrika]], waxaana si rasmi ah loogu aqoonsaday inay tahay lingua frankiga [[Bulshada Bariga Afrika]].<ref>[http://www.eac.int/treaty/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=206&Itemid=331 Development and Promotion of Extractive Industries and Mineral Value Addition, East African Community</ref>

